      <title>Axis Bank 首席执行官表示，印度储备银行将“慢慢来”捍卫卢比</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/usd-inr-rbi-to-play-it-slow-on-defending-rupee-axis-bank-ceo-says</link>
